===Etymology===
* First attested before 1425.
* From {{etyl|frm}} '''and''' {{etyl|la}} {{term|ablatio|ablātiō|a taking away|lang=la}}, from {{term|ablatus|ablātus|removed|lang=la}}, the perfect passive participle of {{term|aufero|auferō|carry away|lang=la}}.
* Compare French {{term|ablation|lang=fr}}.

